com.gwt.ss

Class GwtLogoutSuccessHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gwt.ss.GwtLogoutSuccessHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean, org.springframework.security.web.authentication.logout.LogoutSuccessHandler, org.springframework.web.context.ServletContextAware

    public class GwtLogoutSuccessHandler
extends Object
implements org.springframework.security.web.authentication.logout.LogoutSuccessHandler, org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean, org.springframework.web.context.ServletContextAware
    Assign to <logout success-handler-ref="hander-reference"/> fot handle logout action.
    When logout from GWT RPC, just void message return. If logout from normal URL will redirect page to logoutSuccessUrl.
    建立本類別實例並設定到<logout success-handler-ref="實例參照"/> 以處理登錄作業，
    當使用GWT RPC進行登出時，本顯別會回應GWT RPC程式。
    若使用正常址址登出，則頁面會回轉到logoutSuccessUrl
